data.text:
Britannia Milk Bikis Biscuits is one of the most nutritious biscuit brands. Make Your Tea times Healthy with a packet of Britannia Milk Biscuits. trusted Brand By the Mothers For Child growth nutrition over the year and it has become an important part of their child's nutrition. Britannia Milk Bikis is fully loaded with Healthy Milk Protein Each Milk Bikis biscuit is crispy and light is packed with the goodness of Vitamins and Minerals that makes for healthier teatimes. So go ahead, Best With a cup of tea/Coffee or to satisfy mid-meal hunger. Enjoy a light Crispy crunchy & nutritious bite, Suitable for all ages.

Ingredients: Refined Wheat Flour (Maida), Sugar, Refined Oil, Invert Sugar Syrup, Raising Agents, Milk Solids, Iodised Salt, Vitamins, Calcium Salt, Nature and Artificial Favour- Milk, Butter & Vanilla.

Features:

Best Choice For tea/coffeeTime

Perfect For All Type Of Diet

Rich with dietary fiber

100% vegetarian

No trans fat or cholesterol

Best quality product

All-Time Favorite Snacks

How to Use: Enjoy the delicious flavors in every bite of these ready-to-eat milk bikies biscuits.

Package: Packet

Manufactured by: Britannia Industries Ltd.

Country Of Origin: Product of India

Product Weight: 78 Grams

Storage Instructions: Store in a cool and dry place

I recommend this product to anyone looking for a balm to help with pain. It is strong without excess heat or a burning sensation. It does the job; it's a good product.
